																aria-expanded="false">카테고리 선택</button>
															<div class="dropdown-menu"
																aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton">
																<a class="dropdown-item" href="javascript:;"
																	onclick="buildList(event,'All')">전체</a> <a
